{"TopicId":203297,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"What are mobile launch pads?","CreatedByName":"Star-Eagle","CreatedById":151995,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-25T10:31:54Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Star-Eagle","CreatedById":151995,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-25T10:31:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was looking through the 1.12 launch announcement and I noticed the part about mobile launch pads but I haven\u0027t seen anything about them before. Could anyone explain to a poor kerb who\u0027s been living under a rock what they are?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"eekee","CreatedById":211180,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-25T11:04:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EI missed that one, but now I\u0027m super-curious! If... \u003Cem\u003Eif\u003C/em\u003E they allow launching new craft, and \u003Cem\u003Eif \u003C/em\u003Ethey can be taken to other bodies and incorporated into bases, I will be a very very \u003Cem\u003Every\u003C/em\u003E happy kerbal! \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was thinking of a mod, if it exists or if my skills were up to making it: Honest Harry\u0027s Construction Company, in which you take parts to a location and build your base, then tell the mod to make it a site, optionally with launch facilities. \u003Cem\u003EIf\u003C/em\u003E mobile launch pads are what I hope, then between them and the ground anchors we won\u0027t need a mod to do this. But would it work for launching planes... Yes, with a little ingenuity.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xavven","CreatedById":100398,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-06-25T13:14:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, here are the relevant notes in the patch:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRejoice and explore the Kerbal universe once more\u2026 you might even encounter some of the new easter eggs and unlockable launch sites scattered around the solar system. Are you ready?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n* Fix Mobile Launch sites where all the legs will now try to extend if one does not find a ground collision.\u003Cbr\u003E\n* Fix Mobile Launch Sites could end up with a null reference for positionMobileLaunchsite.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Krazy1","CreatedById":203523,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-08T01:53:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso curious what these are. So if they\u0027re new... why did they list bugfixes for them in the same release?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:blink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_blink.png\u0022 title=\u0022:blink:\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Krazy1","CreatedById":203523,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-08T07:51:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223994859\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221624619049\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022211180\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022eekee\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 6/25/2021 at 4:04 AM, eekee said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was thinking of a mod, if it exists\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMaybe different than what you were thinking but there\u0027s this:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002257176\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6497600254\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/54284-18-110-extraplanetary-launchpads-v683/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:195px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNever tried it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrdinaryKerman","CreatedById":208637,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-08T08:04:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224001214\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221625709183\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022203523\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Krazy1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Krazy1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso curious what these are. So if they\u0027re new... why did they list bugfixes for them in the same release?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:blink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_blink.png\u0022 title=\u0022:blink:\u0022\u003E\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe launch sites are new, but the \u0027extra launch pads\u0027 mechanism has long been a part of the MH DLC. They just added that\u00A0functionality to the stock game in 1.12.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"he77789","CreatedById":212909,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-19T06:51:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224001303\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221625731493\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022208637\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022OrdinaryKerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/8/2021 at 4:04 PM, OrdinaryKerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe launch sites are new, but the \u0027extra launch pads\u0027 mechanism has long been a part of the MH DLC. They just added that\u00A0functionality to the stock game in 1.12.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell in the MH DLC there are only launch sites on Kerbin, but in the patch notes, it specifies that the new launch sites are all over the solar system...?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KerikBalm","CreatedById":91917,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-19T08:22:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224006713\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221626677511\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022212909\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022he77789\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, he77789 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell in the MH DLC there are only launch sites on Kerbin, but in the patch notes, it specifies that the new launch sites are all over the solar system...?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat I see:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://support.privatedivision.com/hc/en-us/articles/4402747185683--Kerbal-Space-Program-Patch-Notes-1-12\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://support.privatedivision.com/hc/en-us/articles/4402747185683--Kerbal-Space-Program-Patch-Notes-1-12\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cul style=\u0022background-color:#ffffff;color:#222222;font-size:15px;padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cli\u003E\nFix Mobile Launch sites where all the legs will now try to extend if one does not find a ground collision.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\nFix Mobile Launch Sites could end up with a null reference for positionMobileLaunchsite.\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso here:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/1.12\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/1.12\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere is this supposed reference specifying that the launch sites are all over the solar system?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"he77789","CreatedById":212909,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-19T09:26:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224006727\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221626682977\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002291917\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KerikBalm\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, KerikBalm said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhat I see:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://support.privatedivision.com/hc/en-us/articles/4402747185683--Kerbal-Space-Program-Patch-Notes-1-12\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://support.privatedivision.com/hc/en-us/articles/4402747185683--Kerbal-Space-Program-Patch-Notes-1-12\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso here:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/1.12\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/wiki/1.12\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere is this supposed reference specifying that the launch sites are all over the solar system?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nQuote\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022background-color:#e6e8e9;color:#2d3134;font-size:15px;\u0022\u003ERejoice and explore the Kerbal universe once more\u2026 you might even encounter some of the new easter eggs and \u003Cstrong\u003Eunlockable launch sites scattered around the solar system\u003C/strong\u003E. Are you ready?\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"OrdinaryKerman","CreatedById":208637,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-07-19T12:16:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224006733\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221626686773\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022212909\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022he77789\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, he77789 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe easter eggs are scattered all over the system. Launch sites are for Kerbin only.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"tg626","CreatedById":112361,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-28T06:10:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know this is old but it is also unanswered.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMobile Launchpad appears to be what Squad calls the square pad with a ramp on one side which is used as a launch pad everywhere that isn\u0027t \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThese are all on Kerbin. Originally it was used for the additional launch sites added by Making History, and later for all the discoverable ones added in v1.12\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe \u0022mobile\u0022 part of the name simply refers to its cosmetic appearance, it is in fact very stationary and unmovable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-28T15:23:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224266488\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221679983858\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022112361\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022tg626\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n9 hours ago, tg626 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know this is old but it is also unanswered.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMobile Launchpad appears to be what Squad calls the square pad with a ramp on one side which is used as a launch pad everywhere that isn\u0027t \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003E\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003EKSC\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/abbr\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThese are all on Kerbin. Originally it was used for the additional launch sites added by Making History, and later for all the discoverable ones added in v1.12\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe \u0022mobile\u0022 part of the name simply refers to its cosmetic appearance, it is in fact very stationary and unmovable.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was about to say exactly that! Also these launch pads are the ones you add in missions (with MH).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-28T20:26:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224266609\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680016986\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022217956\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nazalassa\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, Nazalassa said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was about to say exactly that!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHard to claim being ninja\u2019d if you wait two years to reply\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;p\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/971609041_P.png\u0022 title=\u0022;p\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nazalassa","CreatedById":217956,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-03-29T11:23:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224266731\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022203297\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221680035191\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002264714\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Gargamel\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 hours ago, Gargamel said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHard to claim being ninja\u2019d if you wait two years to reply\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022;p\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/971609041_P.png\u0022 title=\u0022;p\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNah, only nine hours and thirteen minutes... \u003Cspan\u003E:D\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}